candidates master's degree candidates suse's commencement speaker this year is tbd conferral of degrees eamonn callan will read the name and dissertation title for graduating doctoral students as they walk across the stage doctoral students will be hooded by their advisor and master's students by their program director reception warm hors d oeuvres champagne and non alcoholic beverages will be served immediately following the ceremony in the oak grove behind the seating area some tips to make the ceremony more enjoyable dress for the heat light clothing under gown is advisable sun block is recommended comfortable close toed shoes are recommended for walking in the oak grove there is debris from the trees in the diploma ceremony site please direct questions regarding commencement to suse academic services commencement important information for graduating students guest information faculty information day of information for graduates speaker information june 17 2012 9 30am stanford commencement ceremony 12 00pm faculty line up in cap & gown at west oval grove 12 30pm procession begins 12 30pm suse diploma ceremony faculty sit on stage 2 00pm reception in west oval grove stanford university school of education 485 lasuen mall stanford ca 94305 3096 tel 650 723 2109 copyright 2012 stanford university all rights reserved terms of use copyright complaints site map contact us helpsu suse it axess academic calendar stanford bulletin office of the registrar edmail stanfordwho stanfordyou login connect with us on facebook connect with us on twitter connect with us on youtube connect with us on flickr make a gift now
